## All Public Types with Signatures

### `pg::ImGuiLayer`

```cpp
// Constructor — registers the layer with the debug name "ImGuiLayer".
ImGuiLayer();

// Destructor — trivial; cleanup is driven by OnDetach().
~ImGuiLayer();

// Initialises the ImGui context, fonts, style, and Win32/DX11 backends.
// Sets m_Attached = true on success.
virtual void OnAttach() override;

// Shuts down DX11 backend, Win32 backend, and destroys the ImGui context.
// Sets m_Attached = false.
virtual void OnDetach() override;

// Opens a new ImGui frame (must be called before any widget calls this frame).
virtual void Begin() override;

// Finalises and submits all ImGui draw data for the current frame.
virtual void End() override;

// Returns true after a successful OnAttach() and before OnDetach().
bool IsAttached();
```

