## Dependencies on Other Modules

| Dependency | Symbol used | Why |
|---|---|---|
| `Pigeon/Core/Layer.h` | `pg::Layer` | Base class |
| `Pigeon/Core/Application.h` | `pg::Application::Get()` | Access to window and graphics context |
| `Platform/DirectX11/Dx11Context.h` | `pg::Dx11Context` | Retrieve `ID3D11Device*` and `ID3D11DeviceContext*` |
| `Platform/Windows/WindowsWindow.h` | Included transitively | Needed for `HWND` retrieval via `GetNativeWindow()` |
| `Pigeon/Core/KeyCodes.h` | Included | Present in the translation unit; not actively referenced in the current implementation |
| `<imgui.h>` | Dear ImGui core | Context, IO, style, frame management |
| `<backends/imgui_impl_dx11.h>` | DX11 backend | `ImGui_ImplDX11_*` functions |
| `<backends/imgui_impl_win32.h>` | Win32 backend | `ImGui_ImplWin32_*` functions |

The module is **not used** in the `Testing` configuration. `Application::Data` conditionally excludes `m_ImGuiLayer` and `Application::Init()` skips registration when `TESTS_ENABLED` is defined.

